              "settings": {
                "title": "<body>\n\n\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Vaama Story Section</title>\n  <style>\n\n    .section {\n         background: url(https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/About-us.png?v=1747485156) no-repeat bottom / cover;\n    height: 900px;\n    display: flex\n;\n    align-items: end;\n    justify-content: center;\n    position: relative;\n    }\n\n    .glass-box {\n      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n      border-radius: 15px;\n      padding: 30px;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      color: #fff;\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n margin-bottom: 30px\n    }\n\n    .glass-box h2 {\n      margin-top: 0;\n      font-size: 24px;\n      font-weight: bold;\n     color: white;\n     text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .glass-box p {\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n.two-column {\n    display: flex;\n  gap: 30px;\n   font-family: mickir;\n  \n}  \n\n\n@media(max-width: 767px){\n.glass-box {\n      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n      border-radius: 15px;\n      padding: 20px;\n      max-width: 300px;\n      color: #fff;\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n margin-bottom: 30px\n    }\n.two-column {\n    display: block;\n  gap: 10px;\n   font-family: mickir;\n  \n}  \n.glass-box p {\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n}\n}\n  </style>\n\n\n  <section class=\"section\">\n    <div class=\"glass-box\">\n      <h2>The Vaama Story</h2>\n      <div class=\"two-column\">\n      <p>Vaama Jewellery emerged from a simple yet powerful vision: to change how people experience fine jewellery through accessibility and education. We founded our brand on the belief that exquisite diamond craftsmanship should be a standard and not a privilege. By focusing exclusively on lab-grown diamonds of EF color and VVS clarity, we make premium quality accessible to more people. Transparency stands at the heart of everything we do.</p>\n      <p>We believe that understanding what makes a diamond valuable enables confidence in your choice. That’s why we’re committed to educating our customers about diamond quality, helping you make informed, value-driven decisions for jewellery that lasts a lifetime. Vaama represents a new approach to fine jewellery — one that emphasizes quality, ethical sourcing, and knowledge. It’s about empowering you to create jewellery that’s as meaningful as it is beautiful.</p>\n   </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</body>",
