t bottom / cover;\n    height: 600px;\n    display: flex\n;\n    align-items: end;\n    justify-content: center;\n    position: relative;\n}\n}\n  </style>\n\n\n  <section class=\"section\">\n    <div class=\"glass-box\">\n      <h2>The Vaama Story</h2>\n      <div class=\"two-column\">\n      <p>Vaama Jewellery emerged from a simple yet powerful vision: to change how people experience fine jewellery through accessibility and education. We founded our brand on the belief that exceptional diamond craftsmanship isn’t reserved for those with extraordinarily big pockets. By focusing exclusively on lab-grown diamonds of D color and VVS clarity, we make premium quality accessible to more people. Transparency stands at the heart of everything we do.</p>\n      \n   </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</body>",
