              "settings": {
                "title": "<body>\n\n\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>Jewellery Section</title>\n  <style>\n\n\n    .jewellery-section {\n      display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n    gap: 40px;\n    padding: 60px 40px;\n    border-top: 0px solid #f2d1cf;\n    border-bottom: 0px solid #f2d1cf;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n      text-align: center;\n      border: 0px;\n    }\n\n    .card img {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: auto;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    .card h3 {\n      font-size: 28px;\n    margin: 15px 0 10px;\n    color: #28365B;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    }\n\n    .card p {\n    font-size: 17px;\n    color: #28365B;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0 10px;\n    font-family: 'Mickir';\n}\n  </style>\n\n\n\n  <section class=\"jewellery-section\">\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/DFEYou_11_3.png?v=1746082746\" alt=\"Diamond Image\">\n      <h3>Diamonds For Every You</h3>\n      <p>Because your personality has many colors, and your jewelry should reflect every hue.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/SKR06047_1.png?v=1747485715\" alt=\"Jewellery Expression Image\">\n      <h3>Your Jewellery, Your Personal Expression</h3>\n      <p>Custom-made jewellery that begins with your story and ends with something uniquely yours.</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n\n</body>",
